OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChurch sex abuse: Thousands
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fof paedophiles in French   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FChurch, inquiry says       
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Thousands of paedophiles have operated 
OL,6, within the French Catholic Church since
OL,7, 1950, the head of a panel investigating
OL,8, abuses by church members says.         
OL,10,FJean-Marc Sauve told French media that 
OL,11,Fthe commission had found evidence of   
OL,12,F2,900 to 3,200 abusers - out of a total
OL,13,Fof 115,000 priests and other clerics.  
OL,15,F"That is a minimal estimate," he added.
OL,17,FThe commission is to release a lengthy 
OL,18,Freport on Tuesday. It is based on      
OL,19,Fchurch, court and police archives, as  
OL,20,Fwell as interviews with victims.       
